      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, kept spotless, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one. I\u2019ve truly loved owning this car and I\u2019m sure you will too\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
