    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six and its signature individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary structural concerns. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual shifts with surgical precision, paired with a fresh Sachs clutch and a perfectly dialed Vanos system. Suspension geometry is maintained via OEM+ components, ensuring the factory-spec handling remains razor-sharp. A true turn-key enthusiast piece with zero mechanical deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
