    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to the highest standards since it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring deep, mirror-like paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one, and all interior electronics function with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service binder included with the sale. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives like new, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
